PRODUCT     (S)-4-hydroxymandelonitrile [CPD:C03742];
            NADP+ [CPD:C00006];
            H2O [CPD:C00001]
COMMENT     This enzyme is involved in the biosynthesis of the cyanogenic glucoside dhurrin in sorghum, along with EC 1.14.13.41, tyrosine N-monooxygenase and EC 2.4.1.85, cyanohydrin beta-glucosyltransferase.
